---
title: Saucy Mongolian Beef with Garlicky Vegetables
description: Takeout, Fakeout! Mongolian beef is a Chinese restaurant staple and it’s time to master it in your kitchen. The sticky beef, garlicky vegetables and fragrant rice will fill your tongue with flavour!
